headline: 'Tariffs are starting to bite': Latest inflation, jobs data sparks Wall Street concern over US economy
summary: Stocks have continued to notch record highs this year as investors bet on a resilient economy and minimal fallout from tariff-driven inflation. But this week, both assumptions came under pressure.
